WorkPlace.Name: Protemp A/S
WorkPlace.OrganizationDescription: Protemp er en innovativ og højt specialiseret vikarvirksomhed, der tilbyder fleksible, og kundetilpassede bemandingsløsninger til virksomheder som arbejder med infrastruktur, byggeri, fiber/tele/tv, Industri & produktion, Teknik, Vind & energi. Vi tilbyder kompetente danske håndværkere med høj arbejdsmoral og har mere end 30 års erfaring og ekspertise inden for bemandingsbranchen.

JobPositionInformation.PositionTitle: Protemp A/S looking for workers to demolish buildings in Odense. Duration are 6 months!
JobPositionInformation.Purpose:
Our expectations:

  • Flexible. 
  • Punctual.

We offer:

  • Pension and holiday money.
  • Salary every 14th day. 

 

Opgaverne:

  • You must be fit for fight so you can take part in demolish work.
  • You will need to join an asbestos course. It is paid by us. 
  • The jobsite is in Odense.
  • Start in week 19 or as soon as possible.
  • Duration: 6 months.
  • Salary 150 kr/h

Please send an email to job@protemp.dk or call Stina Holm at 6018 7405.

Please mark your application: "Demolish”
